data.description: Immerse yourself in the tranquility of mountain living in the Crabtree community, situated on 1.4 acres of pure serenity. This well-maintained traditional home, nestled in peaceful surroundings, offers a canvas to infuse with your unique style. The spacious home boasts solid foundations and room for customization. Relish the ample space for gardening, recreation, and four legged friends. Step onto the covered front porch and soak in the breathtaking mountain vistas. Tree trimming will allow for more captivating ridgeline views. The living room is the heart of the home, featuring a timeless stone fireplace that exudes warmth & coziness. The eat-in kitchen welcomes your updates and finishes, making a space that suits your tastes. Enjoy the primary suite on the main level and two additional bedrooms plus a bonus room upstairs, offering flexibility to cater to your needs. Furthermore, the assurance of a new roof installation by Baulken Roof scheduled in November 2023.
